        public static <T extends AutoCloseable> AutoCloseableResource.Wrapper<T> forAutoCloseable​(T closeable)
        Creates a wrapper for an AutoCloseable object.

        This method should not be necessary for JUnit 5.13, as from that version onward AutoCloseable can be used with ExtensionContext.Store directly.

        Type Parameters:
